<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Josefin+Sans:ital,wght@0,100;1,100;1,700&family=Mali:ital,wght@0,200;0,700;1,200&family=Montserrat+Alternates:ital,wght@0,100;1,100;1,700&family=Spectral+SC:ital,wght@0,200;0,700;1,200&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1 class="title">My Website Design System</h1>
    <fieldset class="colors">
        <legend><h1>Colors</h1></legend>
        <div class="box aqua">
            <p>Aqua</p>
            <p>#00FFFF</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box brown">
            <p>Brown</p>
            <p>#A52A2A</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box chartreuse">
            <p>Chartreuse</p>
            <p>#7FFF00</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box cornsilk">
            <p>Cornsilk</p>
            <p>#FFF8DC</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box darkcyan">
            <p>DarkCyan</p>
            <p>#008B8B</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box darkorange">
            <p>Darkorange</p>
            <p>#FF8C00</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box deeppink">
            <p>Deeppink</p>
            <p>#FF1493</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box yellow">
            <p>Yellow</p>
            <p>#FFFF00</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box springgreen">
            <p>SpringGreen</p>
            <p>#00FF7F</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box red">
            <p>Red</p>
            <p>#FF0000</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box blue">
            <p>Blue</p>
            <p>#0000FF</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box gray">
            <p>Gray</p>
            <p>#808080</p>
        </div>
    </fieldset>
    <select name="cars" id="colors">
        <option value="white">White</option>
        <option value="deeppink">Deeppink</option>
        <option value="gray">Gray</option>
        <option value="blue">Blue</option>
        <option value="red">Red</option>
        <option value="springgreen">SpringGreen</option>
        <option value="yellow">Yellow</option>
        <option value="darkorange">Darkorange</option>
        <option value="cornsilk">Cornsilk</option>
        <option value="darkcyan">Darkcyan</option>
        <option value="brown">Brown</option>
        <option value="aqua">aqua</option>
        <option value="chartreuse">Chartreuse</option>
      </select>
    <fieldset class="fonts">
        <legend><h1>Fonts</h1></legend>
        <div class="josefinSans">
            <p class="selector">Josefin Sans</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mali">
            <p class="selector">Mali</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="montserratAlternates">
            <p class="selector">Montserrat Alternate</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="spectralSc">
            <p class="selector">Spectral SC</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
            <p>Almost before we knew it, we had left the ground.</p>
        </div>
    </fieldset>
    <fieldset class="textStyle">
        <legend><h1>Text Style</h1></legend>
        <div>
            <h1>H1: Page Heading</h1>
            <ul>
                <li>Font-weight: 700 (bold)</li>
                <li>Font-size: 26px</li>
                <li>Font-family: Josefin Sans</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h2>H2: Subheading</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Font-weight: 500</li>
                <li>Font-size: 16px</li>
                <li>Font-family: Spectral SC</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>P:Paragraph text</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Font-weight: 100</li>
                <li>Font-size: 14px</li>
                <li>Font-family: Mali</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </fieldset>
    <script src="index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
